<h3>OctoDash Setup</h3>

<p>Welcome to OctoDash v3! Some things are new here</p>

<div data-bind="if: configPaths().length">
	<p>An existing legacy OctoDash config was found. Would you like to migrate it?</p>
	<ul data-bind="foreach: configPaths">
	<li><span data-bind="text: $data" ></span><button data-bind="click: $parent.migrate">Migrate</button></li>
	</ul>
	<p data-bind="if: migrated">Migration Complete!</p>
</div>


<div data-bind="if: legacyInstalled()">
	<p>We have detected a legacy OctoDash install on this system. To convert, please run the following command:</p>
	<p><code>bash <(curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UnchartedBull/OctoDash/plugin-migration/scripts/migrate.sh)</code></p>
</div>


<div data-bind="if: !legacyInstalled()">
	<p>If you would like to configure a Raspberry Pi to launch OctoDash, please run the following command:</p>
	<p><code>bash <(curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UnchartedBull/OctoDash/plugin-migration/scripts/install.sh)</code></p>
</div>